mmaryContaineruniface_104wag1665702672443.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wag1665702672443.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wag1665702672443.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wag1665702672443\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the names of any external graphic filters that you want to use.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wag1665702672443__topic_d144935e1_d144936e1_d144937e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wag1665702672443__p_d144938e1_d144939e1_d144940e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Filter</code>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">A</var>-<var class=\"keyword varname\">Z</var>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FilterName</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wag1665702672443__section_o34_55d_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d310367e71\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"wag1665702672443__ul_wyl_w5d_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wag1665702672443__li_d50468e1_d50469e1_d50470e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">A-Z</var>—is the external filter you have defined with an image type of IA\n          through IZ. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wag1665702672443__li_d50471e1_d50472e1_d50473e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FilterName</var>—specifies the name of the external filter. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wag1665702672443__table_d17633e1_d17634e1_d17635e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">None</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nvl1665702672374.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nvl1665702672374.html\" title=\"The [graphic filters] section of the initialization file specifies the graphic filter DLLs that allow Uniface to support particular image file formats.\">[graphic filters]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wag1665702672443__section_yyd_z5d_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d310367e132\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If you intend to write your own image filters for use with Microsoft Windows 95, Microsoft\n        Windows NT, or Windows 2000, ensure that they are ALDUS Windows compliant. Export the\n        functions defined in your filters using the <code class=\"ph codeph\">_declspec (dllexport)</code>\n        convention.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533264\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533264\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Filter Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the names of any external graphic filters that you want to use. Filter { A - Z } = FilterName Arguments A-Z —is the external filter you have defined with an image type of IA through IZ. FilterName —specifies the name of the external filter. Default value: None File section: [graphic filters] Description If you intend to write your own image filters for use with Microsoft Windows 95, Microsoft Windows NT, or Windows 2000, ensure that they are ALDUS Windows compliant. Export the functions defined in your filters using the _declspec (dllexport) convention. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}